title: Showstoppers
description: Showstoppers was released on the RCA label. A collection of 20 songs from Broadway show recordings made between 1909 and 1941. This features such stars as Fanny Brice, Al Jolson, George M. Cohan, Beatrice Lillie, Helen Morgan, Paul Robeson, Eddie Cantor, Ethel Merman, Fred Astaire, Noel Coward, Cole Porter, and Gertrude Lawrence. ~ William Ruhlmann. Showstoppers contains a single disc with 20 songs
